    • Enum Constant Summary

      Enum Constants 
      Enum Constant and Description
      ALL
      This download-strategy loads every data of your system, regardless of your current position.
      AROUNDME
      This downlaod-strategy is necessary if you have a lot of blulocs in your system -> just the blulocs in a radius of 1km around the current position will be loaded If you want to use this strategy, it is necessary to enable location-tracking in android-settings.

    • Enum Constant Detail

      • ALL

        public static final DownloadStrategy ALL
        This download-strategy loads every data of your system, regardless of your current position. This can cause problems on the device if there is a lot of data in your system. In this case use DownloadStrategy.AROUNDME

      • AROUNDME

        public static final DownloadStrategy AROUNDME
        This downlaod-strategy is necessary if you have a lot of blulocs in your system -> just the blulocs in a radius of 1km around the current position will be loaded If you want to use this strategy, it is necessary to enable location-tracking in android-settings. Only blulocs with a set postion will be downloaded.
